<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Deployed by Kelloysrtck</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a, #1e293b);
            color: #f8fafc;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.37);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #38bdf8;
        }

        p {
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            background-color: #0284c7;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(2, 132, 199, 0.4);
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #64748b;
        }

        footer span {
            color: #38bdf8;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>Halo Dunia!</h1>
        <p>Website ini telah berhasil diluncurkan dan siap untuk digunakan. Silakan edit file ini untuk mulai membangun proyek luar biasamu.</p>
        <div class="badge">Status: Active</div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        Deployed by <span>Kelloysrtck</span> &copy; 2026
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
